<h2><a class="listing" style="link" href="/en/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Selected-publications/African-Journal-on-Food-Agriculture-Nutrition-and-Development-AJFAND-2007-Vol-7-no-6" title="African Journal on Food, Agriculture, Nutrition and Development (AJFAND), 2007, Vol 7 no 6" alt="link">African Journal on Food, Agriculture, Nutrition and Development (AJFAND), 2007, Vol 7 no 6</a></h2>

	
					<p> The articles in this issue of AJFAND include:  

 
 Changes in physicochemical and sensory characteristics of smoke-dried fish species stored at ambient temperature (by John Daramola et al.); 
 
