						<p><div class="item">
<h2><a class="listing" style="link" href="/en/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Selected-publications/The-True-Cost-of-Agrofuels-Food-Forests-and-Climate" title="The True Cost of Agrofuels: Food, Forests and Climate" alt="link">The True Cost of Agrofuels: Food, Forests and Climate</a></h2>

	
					<p> 
This report examines the impact of agrofuels development, with particular emphasis on forests and forest dependent peoples. This emphasis on forests is critical for several reasons including that of regulating climate.Source: Global Forest Coalition, 2007 </p>
							<p><span class="date">7/01/2008</span></p>
	<div class="cnt">
	<a class="link" href="/en/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Selected-publications/The-True-Cost-of-Agrofuels-Food-Forests-and-Climate">Read more...</a>
